name: Tonight
detailedForecast: Snow likely and areas of blowing snow before 10pm. Mostly cloudy, with a low around 20. Northwest wind 9 to 17 mph, with gusts as high as 35 mph. Chance of precipitation is 70%. New snow accumulation of less than half an inch possible.
